CONTEXT FlipTypeMismatchCheck IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT FlipTypeMismatchCheck
{+ Test that flip operator fails when result signature doesn't match expected type.
   This verifies the type checker correctly rejects r~[B*A] when [A*C] is expected. +}

RELATION r[A*B]
RELATION result[A*C]

RULE testFlipFail: result = r~

ENDCONTEXT
